Linda Osifo (amụrụ ya na Ụbọchị iri abụọ na asaá na ọnwa asaa Julaị n'afọ1991) ọ bụ onye Naijiria na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-eme telivishọn. Ọ bụ onye nke abụọ na Miss Nigeria Entertainment Canada 2011 na onye nke abụọ n'asọmpi ịma mma Miss AfriCanada n'afọ 2011
N'afọ 2015, a họpụtara Linda maka onyinye ELOY maka ọrụ ya na usoro ihe nkiri TV: Desperate Housewives Africa nke Ebonylife TV An adaptation nke ABC Studio franchise.
